<li>T. DeGrand and C. DeTar, <i>Lattice Methods for Quantum Chromodynamics</i>, World Scientific 2006.</li>
<li>C. Gattringer and C. B. Lang, <i>Quantum Chromodynamics on the Lattice</i>, Springer 2010.</li>
</ul>
